{"tid":2442541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Bobby Chiu: 關於英國藍屍嘅問題我有咁嘅睇法","createTime":"2021-03-11T12:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T15:47:47.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd27a385dbfbe376c7c3dacfe1501a875e3d1f6b","tid":2442541,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/berialm/posts/3917590348310816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fberialm%2Fposts%2F3917590348310816&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHcemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=40edbd67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/berialm/posts/3917590348310816</a><br />\n<br />\n其實下面講法再配合返2019年區議會選舉結果，基本上係有道理㗎。<br />\n<br />\nBobby Chiu: 關於英國藍屍嘅問題我有咁嘅睇法：<br />\n<br />\n最近同一個被界定左藍屍嘅英國華人傾偈（因為佢曾經留言話香港暴徒），發現佢地原來視野好狹窄，香港發生事時，佢地只能夠睇cctvb及幾份親中媒體，所以佢地主觀上覺得cctvb講嘅就係啱，所以當時留左&ldquo;暴徒&rdquo;嘅留言。<br />\n<br />\n佢同我傾左好耐，小弟發現佢根本心地善良，只係身處英國根本搞唔清楚乜野係真嘅資訊。<br />\n<br />\n我問佢點解唔澄清？佢話一上網就俾人勁鬧，連任何解釋機會都無，算啦，無香港人朋友，日子咪又係一樣咁過。<br />\n<br />\n小弟舉個例子，美國嘅BLM，好多主流媒體話佢地正義，但係如果你細心了解一啲媒體嘅報導，佢地又真係同暴徒無疑。<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得我地應該設立一個機制，容許因為曾經在網上發表過類似藍屍言論嘅英國華人，解釋當日點解會有咁嘅睇法，依家佢有乜野睇法，先至去真正將呢啲在英華人分類，而唔係一見到一個在英華人留言，就搜尋佢以前嘅言論，立刻界定佢係藍屍，其實呢種做法對將來大量移居英國嘅港人並無益處。"},{"pid":"f5e23a4e91aef1d11b7c1468b8b8a4cca8644b77","tid":2442541,"uid":36383,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦屌，有心了解點會唔上連登又冇網管"},{"pid":"0745149d30f46d7aa2a429d19b4d76ec1f940c77","tid":2442541,"uid":25240,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"On9 <br />\n外國都勉強可以當<br />\n但香港經bno status 過去既點會有可能係睇cctvb fake news 先撐警<br />\n大大個721 係度"},{"pid":"d3a3a87b25322eaece843dc39ef0fccf6c5e98a2","tid":2442541,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0745149d30f46d7aa2a429d19b4d76ec1f940c77","tid":2442541,"uid":25240,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"On9 <br />\n外國都勉強可以當<br />\n但香港經bno status 過去既點會有可能係睇cctvb fake news 先撐警<br />\n大大個721 係度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"好明顯佢係嘅BC堆老坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722e1d01c17ffc9736828acd7d3d3b07b2e7ee8e","tid":2442541,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e23a4e91aef1d11b7c1468b8b8a4cca8644b77","tid":2442541,"uid":36383,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦屌，有心了解點會唔上連登又冇網管"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a946063e20e8e5b875e6f9325fd58fc47eb8d76c","tid":2442541,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"722e1d01c17ffc9736828acd7d3d3b07b2e7ee8e","tid":2442541,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e23a4e91aef1d11b7c1468b8b8a4cca8644b77","tid":2442541,"uid":36383,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦屌，有心了解點會唔上連登又冇網管"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b09876743a4460c3e01386672fc8d33a7f58cf2","tid":2442541,"uid":162535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3a3a87b25322eaece843dc39ef0fccf6c5e98a2","tid":2442541,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0745149d30f46d7aa2a429d19b4d76ec1f940c77","tid":2442541,"uid":25240,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:56:09.000Z","msg":"On9 <br />\n外國都勉強可以當<br />\n但香港經bno